{
  "id": "photo-secret",
  "name": "偷拍的照片",
  "category": "photo",
  "description": "一张偷偷拍摄的照片，带有SECRET印章和手写备注",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.03,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "relationship",
        "operator": ">=",
        "value": 60,
        "description": "好感度达到60以上时可能触发"
      },
      {
        "type": "scene",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "日常|休息|独处|安静",
        "description": "日常场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "photoDescription": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "照片内容描述（用于占位符显示）"
    },
    "caption": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "照片标题/说明"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "date",
      "format": "YYYY.MM.DD",
      "description": "拍摄日期"
    },
    "cameraInfo": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "ISO 400 | f/2.8 | 1/125s",
      "description": "相机参数信息"
    },
    "note": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "手写备注内容"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一张偷拍照片的相关信息。\n\n背景信息：\n- 拍摄对象：{{subject}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 拍摄者：{{photographer}}\n\n要求：\n1. 照片描述要温馨有趣，展现拍摄对象的某个瞬间\n2. 标题简短有感情\n3. 手写备注要体现拍摄者的心情\n4. 整体氛围要温馨但不失神秘感\n\n请按以下格式输出：\n照片描述：...\n标题：...\n备注：...",
  "style": {
    "theme": "nostalgic",
    "colors": ["#2c3e50", "#fff", "#888"],
    "mood": "温馨私密"
  },
  "rarity": "uncommon",
  "collectible": true
}